data.title: Anna Lee Movies and Shows
data.meta_description: Learn about Anna Lee on Apple TV. Browse shows and movies that feature Anna Lee including The Sound of Music, The Ghost and Mrs. Muir, and more.
data.text:
The Case of the Unsuitable Uncle

A sailor too poor to pay legal fees makes out a will with bequests of $300,000; guests Sean McClory, Liam Sullivan, Barbara Parkins.

Go Home, Mr. French

Mr. French encounters an old friend while at the park with the twins. Lorna, the nanny for a Duke & Duchess, is visiting in the states. When they are ready to return to England, Mr. French considers returning with her.

Rope Fever

Festus becomes involved with a wounded bank robber and is accused of being his partner.
